annotationA: CR6-interacting factor (CRIF) may play a role in regulating the RNAi pathway by stabilizing the RNAase III enzyme Dcr-2
annotationB: Mitochondrial ribosomal protein L44; Ribonuclease III activity; structural constituent of ribosome; RNA binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitochondrial translation; RNA processing; neurogenesis
